OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FOvernight, it will remain dry with
OL,8,Ffurther clear spells. A little chilly
OL,9,Fin the countryside but not as cold as
OL,10,Frecent nights. Some mist or fog
OL,11,Fpatches possible over the moors
OL,12,Ftowards dawn.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry day
OL,15,Fwith spells of sunshine for much of
OL,16,Fthe region. Patchy cloud likely
OL,17,Ffurther west across Cornwall,
OL,18,Fespecially during the afternoon.
OL,19,FFeeling warm with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
