OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCooler and more changeable on
OL,7,FThursday, with cloudy skies and odd
OL,8,Fspots of rain. Staying unsettled on
OL,9,FFriday and Saturday with rain at
OL,10,Ftimes, mainly on Saturday.
OL,11,FTemperatures nearer average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
